                        <interp inst="t18520202-name-359" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEBSTER</persName>
                  </hi>. These are both bad.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I never was in the woman's house; as for a white shawl, I have never worn one since I have been in London; I was in bed that afternoon; I begged my landlady Mrs. Gray to come here to speak to my innocence; I hope you will give me time to send for her.</p>
